# 03 - NFCU Phishing

## Intro

We can build on the AAFES hypothesis-driven exercise and turn that towards banking. We’ll keep it military-themed. A common military bank is Navy Federal Credit Union. The real site is navyfederal.org.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

Here’s the urlscan search:

[https://urlscan.io/search/#navyfederal.org](https://urlscan.io/search/#navyfederal.org)

![](data:image/png;base64,)

We can use result #4.

[https://urlscan.io/result/019a0722-91be-719a-8aab-09b4879e5a7a/](https://urlscan.io/result/019a0722-91be-719a-8aab-09b4879e5a7a/)

![](data:image/png;base64,)

Note that the page title says page not found. We don’t want to search using that, so we’ll try an image search.

## Pattern

In the transactions tab, click the image button to only see the transactions for images. Next, search for an image name that is likely to be unique to NFCU. We will use the ncua-logo.svg file.

https://urlscan.io/result/019a0722-91be-719a-8aab-09b4879e5a7a/#transactions

![](data:image/png;base64,)

## Action the Pattern

Expand it by clicking the magnifying glass, and then click the Resource Hash link to open a search on the hash.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

That brings us here to a target-rich environment.

https://urlscan.io/search/#hash%3A72b394991c1474bfb8e682e645a7cb0161045450aa810b4c9b66d695300d0f78

![](data:image/png;base64,)

We can see that one scan was submitted by openphish, and one was from phishstats. Also, one has the tag “phishdestroy”. These are good indicators. 

## Validate

I will link and snip a few to show what they look like. For each scan result, take note of the obviously-fake domain name combined with the page title. It is apparent that each domain is a fake that is masquerading as NFCU.

## External Validator

We are skipping the external validator because it is very obvious that these are phishing masquerade sites.
## Summary

We used a new technique to find fake sites. We’ve used the page titles as a pivot a few times, but we pivoted on an image hash on this one. There are many things that can be used for a pivot. The goal of this is to use the easiest. The page title and image hashes are normally the simplest.
